===Transitive verb===
'''to jar''' (jarring, jarred, jarred)
#To [[knock]] or [[strike]] sharply.
#:''He hit it with a hammer, hoping he could '''jar''' it loose.''
#to [[shock]] or [[surprise]].
#:''I think the accident '''jarred''' him, as he hasn't gotten back in a car since.''

